reviewText: I purchased these DVDs to add them to my DVD library, as something that many people could enjoy. So far, the main person enjoying my library is myself, but  that's good too. I do seem to prefer the earlier seasons, but all are good, and the season blooper compilations sometimes surprises as well.

reviewText: I was so upset at the crapy cropped picture and shorter scenes of the Blu-Ray I had to buy the extended versions.  My friend had let me watch these and after I seen the Blu-Ray version I thought I'd get a better version of the series but didn't.  These are the greatest.  Thank you for the quick delivery and the entire package was perfect.
